ion of cGMP is regulated by both the rates of synthesis and degradation via phosphodiesterases (PDEs). The most abundant PDE in the human corpus cavernosum is the cGMPspecific phosphodiesterase type 5 (PDE5); therefore, the inhibition of PDE5 enhances erectile function by increasing the amount of cGMP.','["G04BE09"]','[]'),(7520,'Lopresor 50 mg 40 tab','لوبريسور 50مجم 40 قرص','88','','Antihypertensive selective b blocker','Metoprolol','Novartis','Tab','أقراص','50 mg','4','حالات الضغط المرتفع','','','',1837,'2022-07-28',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'Metoprolol is a selective beta-1 blocker commonly employed as the succinate and tartrate derivatives depending if the formulation is designed to be of immediate release or extended release.[A175159, L5530] The possibility of the generation of these formulations comes from the lower systemic bioavailability of the succinate derivative.[T274] To this date, it is one of the preferred beta-blockers in general clinical guidelines and it is widely prescribed in the Netherlands, New Zealand, and the US.[A175162] Metoprolol was developed since 1969 by US Pharmaceutical Holdings I and FDA approved in 1978.[L5527]','["C07FB02", "C07FX05", "C07FX03", "C07FB13", "C07AB02", "C07BB52", "C07CB02", "C07BB02"]','[]'),(7521,'Lorafast 2.5mg/5ml syrup. 100 ml','لورافاست 2.5 مجم/5مل شراب 100 مل','26','15.5','Antihistamine.antiallergy','Desloratadine','Egyphar','Syrup','شراب','2.5mg','1','','','6224001026485','',1717,'2024-11-16',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'Desloratadine is a second generation, tricyclic antihistamine that which has a selective and peripheral H1-antagonist action. It is the active descarboethoxy metabolite of loratidine (a second generation histamine). Desloratidine has a long-lasting effect and does not cause drowsiness because it does not readily enter the central nervous system.','["R06AX27"]','[]'),(7523,'Sodi crystal 500 mg 30 tab','صودي كريستال 500مجم 30 قرص','58','','Source of sodium','Sodium bicarbonate','Biomak pharm'